"> <p> Ailleurs, sur les internets </p> <ul class=\"social-media-list\"> <li class=\"social-media-item\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/MichaelBlaizot\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Profil Twitter\"><i class=\"fa-twitter fab\"></i></a></li> <li class=\"social-media-item\"><a href=\"https://dribbble.com/MichaelBlaizot\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Profil Pinterest\"><i class=\"fa-dribbble fab\"></i></a></li> <li class=\"social-media-item\"><a href=\"https://medium.com/@michaelblaizot\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Profil Medium\"><i class=\"fa-medium fab\"></i></a></li> <li class=\"social-media-item\"><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/micha%C3%ABl-blaizot-882a3888?trk=hp-identity-name\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Profil Linkedin\"><i class=\"fa-linkedin fab\"></i></a></li> <li class=\"social-media-item\"><a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/mikblaiz/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Profil Instagram\"><i class=\"fa-instagram fab\"></i></a></li> </ul> </div> </nav> </div> </header>  <section id=\"naturamind-projet\" class=\"section-wrapper--pbig start-change\"> <div class=\"container--lg\"> <div class=\"projet\"> <h1 data-aos=\"fade-down\"><small>Naturamind</small><br>Un site internet minimaliste et distingué pour booster la marque montpellieraine de compléments alimentaires. Du bio, du bien-être et du web ! </h1> <ul class=\"projet__tags\" data-aos=\"fade-up\"> <li data-aos=\"fade-down\" data-aos-delay=\"100\"><small>Année</small><br><em>2017</em></li> <li data-aos=\"fade-down\" data-aos-delay=\"200\"><small>Agence</small><br><em>Freelance</em></li> <li data-aos=\"fade-down\" data-aos-delay=\"300\"><small>Compétence #1</small><br><em>UX Design</em></li> <li data-aos=\"fade-down\" data-aos-delay=\"400\"><small>Compétence #2</small><br><em>Direction Artistique</em></li> <li data-aos=\"fade-down\" data-aos-delay=\"500\"><small>Compétence #3</small><br><em>UI Design</em></li> </ul> <picture class=\"projet__figure\"> <source srcset=\"/0755dcfe28b8ebabc9311222a6ea47c9.webp 400w,/bb7ed