67px), (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2) 2340w\n\t\t\t\t\t\" type=\"image/webp\" data-aos=\"fade-up\"> <figure> <img srcset=\"/145fc5a8fe04458f35ba5dcc93dd833d.jpg 400w,/d12cafc1a89e7349f9565f28706454d9.jpg 800w,/3188bc64da4aeddf6d15b522fae7a2e3.jpg 1170w,/f8439f7dd15d052820cbc771c93a6c50.jpg 2340w\" sizes=\"\n\t\t\t\t\t\t(max-width: 375px) 400w,\n\t\t\t\t\t\t(max-width: 375px), (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2) 800w,\n\t\t\t\t\t\t(min-width : 767px) 1170w,\n\t\t\t\t\t\t(min-width : 767px), (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2) 2340w\n\t\t\t\t\t\" src=\"/3188bc64da4aeddf6d15b522fae7a2e3.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"Naturamind - img02\" data-aos=\"fade-up\"> <figcaption>UI Board set du site web</figcaption> </figure> </picture> <picture class=\"projet__figure\"> <source srcset=\"/a8bde6dd9cdb8e74502a4fcfca5aa33e.webp 400w,/b1b0b8079b195b51b347c1012156a933.webp 800w,/10099da7306d20f2a56105841008b36d.webp 1170w,/d45e8d1448d11e0ebae661f9758535c5.webp 2340w\" sizes=\"\n\t\t\t\t\t\t(max-width: 375px) 400w,\n\t\t\t\t\t\t(max-width: 375px), (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2) 800w,\n\t\t\t\t\t\t(min-width : 767px) 1170w,\n\t\t\t\t\t\t(min-width : 767px), (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2) 2340w\n\t\t\t\t\t\" type=\"image/webp\" data-aos=\"fade-up\"> <figure> <img srcset=\"/c6c8a3d1ec9948f10ba4715bb136d428.jpg 400w,/f718907bace40892882564d9f77c3531.jpg 800w,/4fde8e7b0b03b0aaf65434af9fbb6a1e.jpg 1170w,/1070337a68e65f5e7e7e105a0c35a0d0.jpg 2340w\" sizes=\"\n\t\t\t\t\t\t(max-width: 375px) 400w,\n\t\t\t\t\t\t(max-width: 375px), (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2) 800w,\n\t\t\t\t\t\t(min-width : 767px) 1170w,\n\t\t\t\t\t\t(min-width : 767px), (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2) 2340w\n\t\t\t\t\t\" src=\"/4fde8e7b0b03b0aaf65434af9fbb6a1e.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"Naturamind - img03\" data-aos=\"fade-up\"> <figcaption>Arborescence + User Flow</figcaption> </figure> </picture> <picture class=\"projet__figure\"> <source srcset=\"/1b631cfc5e5d13c5b2d37153ad796453.webp 400w,/7c66